        "subject": "LU-3952 nfs: prep op_valid for md_getattr_name",
        "message": "LU-3952 nfs: prep op_valid for md_getattr_name\n\nmdt_getattr_name_lock() tries mdt_raw_lookup() to get object's\nFID by name, which needs RPC request set OBD_MD_FLID in its request\nvalid bit.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I250c6df7e3c5ed9badef7b175c2ea99ebbcc684e\n"
